TEXT: One morning, when [Gregor Samsa]_n0 woke from troubled dreams, [he]_p0 found [himself]_p1 transformed in [his]_p2 bed into a horrible vermin. [He]_p3 lay on [his]_p4 armour-like back, and if [he]_p7 lifted [his]_p5 head a little [he]_p8 could see [his]_p5 brown belly, slightly domed and divided by arches into stiff sections. The bedding was hardly able to cover [it]_p9 and seemed ready to slide off any moment. [His]_p10 many legs, pitifully thin compared with the size of the rest of him, waved about helplessly as [he]_p11 looked.
